title: 'Excellent value for money'
body: 'I was a bit uncertain before ordering but satisfied completely after using the belt for over a week.  Size - as expected Finish - very good Belt material - looks and feels artificial but at this price point great value Buckle - Excellent finish and works well  Overall a great value for money'

title: 'Aesthetic and Sturdy as per first impression'
body: 'The belt arrived one day earlier than the delivery date so kudos to the seller and Amazon. The belt looks and works well will update after a few months of use.'

title: 'Happy with the product .. recommended'
body: 'Firstly impressive packaging. Belt looks exactly as ordered. Finishing is excellent and looks pretty upmarket. Its too early to comment on durability but since it has no holes  bye bye to those fixed length setups and punching new holes as you grow/shrink. The grip in the buckle seems comfortably tight for now but will know once used for a couple of months. Overall at this price range its definitely good value for money. Wish little rahul grows a bit taller. :-)'

title: 'Good quality buckle'
